<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Abrir App Expo</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 50px;
    }
    a {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 15px 25px;
      background-color: #2d89ef;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    a:hover {
      background-color: #1b5fbd;
    }
    .qr-container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 40px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
    .qr-box img {
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
      border: 2px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Abrir o Jogo no Expo</h1>
  <p>Clique no botão abaixo para abrir o aplicativo:</p>
  <a href="exp://u.expo.dev/933fd9c0-1666-11e7-afca-d980795c5824?runtime-version=exposdk%3A54.0.0&channel-name=production&snack=%40alifer2211%2F10a2f8&snack-channel=wUByqDY9oh">
    Abrir no Expo Go
  </a>

  <div class="qr-container">
    <div class="qr-box">
      <img src="qr1.png" alt="QR Code 1">
    </div>
    <div class="qr-box">
      <img src="qr2.png" alt="QR Code 2">
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
